E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Please tell me this is over. I'll never look at a guy in leather in the same way.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~请告诉我完事了。我再也没法直视穿皮衣的人了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~His driver's getting far too far ahead of himself, huh. Delusions of adequacy, I suppose.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~他的司机太把自己当回事了，呵。自我意识过剩了属于是。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You don't know everything, do you, Luis?
~z~It's time for a change and that change is me, honey.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~是时候改变了，我就是那个变量，亲爱的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I'm privy to the fact that the coke in your nose and the 'roids in your veins
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我还知道你鼻子里的可卡因和血管里的类固醇

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~who's using Tony, and you only gonna be hanging around for two to three months, before Tony moves on to another chump.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~只想利用Tony。顶多再跳两三个月，Tony就会另寻新欢了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Take us out to East Hook then, Luis. Come on! Chop. Chop.
~z~We need to get out of here. Come on, Luis.
~z~Oh yeah, I forgot. You just snort the money, you don't know where it comes from.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~哦对，差点忘了。你不在乎钱的来头，能买到可卡因就行。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I'm privy enough to know that you're a piece of shit
~z~I think you got things the wrong way around there, bro.
~z~"We've got no money left. They're going to repossess everything. Ughh, my life is shit."
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~「我们没钱了。这些都要被收走了。啊，我的人生完了。」

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~On, off, off, on. What can I say, that pathetic sack of shit needs me, and I need amusement.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~分，分，合，合。我能说啥，那可悲的窝囊废需要我，而我也需要乐子。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~are gonna send you worse out of control real soon.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~迟早会让你尝到自己种下的恶果。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I just see you guys come and then disappear and the world keeps turning and the clubs keep running.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我就看着你们来来去去，地球照转，夜店照开。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I think my talents would be better spent full time at the company.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我愿意把才干完全奉献给贵公司。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Jesus, the amount of time it takes to turn him back into the Gay Tony people pay to hang out with,
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~天，费了多少工夫才把他变回那个人见人爱的基佬Tony，

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~See what I mean, always so serious. Don't worry, for once.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~看到没，总是那么严肃。这次就别多虑了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Tony's skimmed ten percent off the agreed amount so we'll have some spending money.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~Tony私吞了货款的一成，当作我们的零用钱。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Listen, Luis, no offense, but I don't know how much I'm allowed to tell you.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~听着，Luis，无意冒犯，但我不知道能跟你透露多少。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~That what you thinking about, you piece of shit. Get out of my face. Goodbye.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~你就想着这些是吧，你这人渣。从我面前消失。再见。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I mean, he's always in such a mood when he sees you. Whinge. Whinge. Whinge.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~真的，见到你他就没好心情了。惨啊，惨啊，惨啊。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I don't like the sound of this, bro.
~z~You the guy who keeps him up at night and feeds him pills so he's catatonic all day long. He don't need that shit.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~是你让他彻夜狂欢，用药喂得他神经兮兮。他不需要这些。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I'm also privy to the fact that you gonna be some fat trailer park queen back in the Midwest before you hit thirty.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我更知道不到三十岁你就会流落中西部，活成拖车公园里的黄脸婆。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Oh, Lou Lou. You are such a downer.
~z~I ain't jealous. I feel bad for you. If you weren't so damn creepy, I'd feel pity.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我不是嫉妒，兄弟，是替你悲哀。要不是你太恶心，我还挺同情你的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Really? I mean, how much information are you privy to? You're just the fucking driver, after all.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~可以吗？我说，你配知道多少？就一开车的而已。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You're fucking jealous, Luis. Pent up because you are not getting your hands on my man.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~你他妈就是嫉妒，Luis。抢不到我的男友就只能抱怨。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I'll go with the driver and try to rebuild my psyche. Luis, you take Evan.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我坐司机的车，好好缓一缓。Luis，你来载Evan。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I, on the other hand, am the fucking idiot who keeps him alive and out of jail.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我就不一样了，忙着帮他擦屁股保命，省得坐牢。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~How the fuck should I know? I'm the looks, not the accountant.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我他妈怎么知道？我是他情人，又不是会计。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~It's just you and me left, Luis. Huh huh. Let's split it all - fifty fifty?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~就剩咱俩了，Luis。 *抽泣* 把钱分了吧，五五开？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You take Evan, Lou. I'll go with the driver. I could do with not talking.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~你带Evan，Lou。我跟司机。我想先安静会儿。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~If you say something nice, I'll think about it.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~嘴巴够甜的话，我会考虑一下的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I could get used to you driving me around. I might have to do it more often.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我会习惯由你接送的，可能得多找你。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I ain't no downer, you fucking moron, I'm just trying to stop Tony from throwing his life and our business away.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我才不是来扫兴的，蠢货。我是在阻止Tony搞砸自己的生活和事业。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Ughh, that attitude's not gonna get you anywhere, sweetie. You better say something nice to me.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~唉，这可不是求人办事的态度啊，宝贝。嘴要放甜一点。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~What's this? Why is the driver talking to me? Hello! I don't speak to the help.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~什么情况？车夫在跟我说话吗？听好！我不跟下人说话的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Now, tell me what the fuck we doing right now!
~z~Fuck. Blow them up with these, Luis. I really don't want to die today.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~操。用这个炸飞他们，Luis。我今天真不想死。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~What do you mean, Evan, tell me everything you know.
~z~I thought we froze your allowance? What with the economy and all.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我们没把你的零花钱停掉？这都经济危机了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, we need someone to lick out the toilet bowls.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~好，店里正好缺一个舔马桶的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Here's where Tony said to meet him.
~z~Take these bombs, Luis. I don't want to die here.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~拿上这些黏弹，Luis。我不想死在这儿。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for this Tony. I was thinking we needed more excitement. Let's do it then.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~谢谢啊，Tony。刚才我还嫌不够刺激。来吧。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~and you don't get where he is by signing shit over to a piece of pumped up ass.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~不可能签个字就把一切转让给你这个傻逼。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Yo, E, I thought you and Tony was split up.
~z~You see, Luis. This is why I need to play a bigger role in the organisation. Things fuck up when you're involved.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~你看吧，Luis。所以才需要我来接手一切。你参与的事情总会搞砸。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Keep them off us, Luis. Use these bombs.
~z~I'll go with the driver, Lou. I need a bit of peace. Take Evan for me.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我跟司机一块，Lou。需要清净一会儿。你负责带Evan。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~No, Evan, they fuck up when you're involved. Now get out of my face. So long, asshole.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~不，Evan，有你在才会搞砸的。从我面前消失。再见，混蛋。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~We got some severely inhibited viewing with this thing.
~z~Help us. Shit. What the fuck has Rocco gotten us into?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~救救咱们，操。Rocco都找的什么破事啊？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~The money could be Rocco's, it could be Gracie's, who cares? We're getting some ice, baby.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~钱可能是Rocco的，也可能是Gracie的，重要吗？我们要换的可是钻石，宝贝。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I deserve that allowance hike and more! I should be on the payroll, just like you.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我的零花钱可不是白涨的！就该像你一样有工资拿。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Ay Dios mio. Where did Tony get that kind of cash, bro?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我的天哪。Tony哪来的这么多钱，兄弟？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I guess we doing this. And thanks for the warning, T. really appreciated.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~看来必须动手了。多谢你提醒，T。非常感谢。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I got you, you son of a bitch.
~z~Thinking about becoming a partner in the club business, too. Tony needs all the help he can get.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我还想当夜店生意的合伙人。Tony需要更多帮手。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I should have people to handle this shit for me.
~z~Someone must have tipped these bikers off.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~肯定有人放风给这帮飞车党了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I can't see shit through this windscreen.
~z~Ha, we got you in the bag now, motherfucker!
~z~We're buying diamonds. Two million dollars' worth.
~z~Shit, limos. I know I had a big night when there's one of these stupid things waiting.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~操，礼车。看见它我就知道昨晚玩得有多大了。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Yeah. We can see where the business has got to with your involvement.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~是啊。大家都知道生意被你搞成了什么鬼样。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You can get Tony fucked up like no one else can, Evan. That nice enough?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~你干翻Tony的本事无人能比，Evan。这样够不够？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Fraid not, Lou Lou. I got a hike as part of my getting back together deal.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~还真没有，Lou Lou。涨零花钱是复合的条件之一。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~What are we doing going to the docks in East Hook?
~z~I've got to warn you Luis, I'm going to be very hands-on and you're not going to like all of my changes.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我警告你，Luis，到时候我事必躬亲，你不会喜欢那些变化的。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You musta had Tony under the influence of some serious shit when he said he'd take you on,
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~得下多猛的药才能让Tony跟你搭伙做生意，

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Left me with my favorite person. Perfect.
~z~Yes, you are! And the last thing a club owner needs is to stop being fun.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~是，没错！夜店老板最不需要的就是停止作乐。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Aww, sweet. Thank you, Luis. Tony is more fun when I'm around. What do you want to know?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~噢，过奖。谢谢你，Luis。我在的时候Tony更开心。你想知道什么？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I was looking forward to him upgrading. You know, to a newer, less annoying model.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我还盼着他找个新欢呢。找个没那么烦人的模特。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~because it ain't happening. The guy's been in business since '87,
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~想想都不可能。他是1987年入的行，

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~Whoop! Whoop! Gonna hit the shops today, baby.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~呼！呼！可以去商场血拼了，宝贝。

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~You know we're heading to the docks in East Hook.
~z~I forgot about ordering these limos. Coke makes me real classy, don't it?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我还雇了礼车吗？可卡因让我挥金如土啊，是吧？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~I know that money can't be his unless he borrowed it. Where's it from?
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~他绝对掏不出两百万，只能靠借。哪来的钱？

E2T7AUD.original: ~z~We paid for these limos, so we're gonna take them.
E2T7AUD.translated: ~z~我们雇了礼车，不能当成摆设。
